<article id="post-979" class="post-979 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-costa-rica category-general tag-business tag-san-jose">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/05/costa-rican-interviews-day-1/" rel="bookmark">Costa Rican Interviews, Day 1</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>A tropical depression in the north of the country has created our weather woes of the last few days, and a heck of a downpour this morning.<br />
Following our usual breakfast run, Joaquin arrived to pick the three of us up at 8:30 to take us downtown to the CIS / Rapp Collins office to interview candidates for our new office. We had a lot of people on the list, and we all knew it was going to be a long day.<br />
