		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/04/web-20-expo-designing-for-a-web-of-data/" rel="bookmark">Web 2.0 Expo: Designing for a Web of Data</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Only session of the morning. We break for lunch, then more sessions this afternoon. Sorry for all the delays in getting these posted. It seems that while the wireless strength to connect is pretty good (there are hubs everywhere), the pipe allowing 3,000+ connections out all at once blows. I swear there&#8217;s a router around here on fire trying to handle all that traffic.<br />
